node.text:
Sketch timecodes:
5:18 - Benderology 101
10:55 - Corona Ad Parody
14:51 - DeHorn Pill
18:30 - Sunday Morning (I'm Hungover) performed by @jacksonbreitmusic

If you listen to all 20 minutes of this episode and still don't find it funny, DM us personally @maxwellredington @jbfresh and tell us we suck. Or if you find it funny, tell us you liked it. That's an option, too. Probably more likely to respond to those.

Opening song is "Crackin' a Cold One" by @thelewddudes

Big shoutouts to @allthingscomedy @kirkfox @courtneypauroso @picturesofgrant @mikewtrapp @evanjwatkins @jimmyblueberry @_mallorykm_

Follow @welcometofriday.pod for more.

Created by the Barrett brothers 🤝

node.text:
Looks like he was hosting a sick pregame. At least it sounded pretty chill from how @haileesteinfeld described it. A bunch of phone towers in our area got knocked down recently so our service has been spotty. Probably why Dooley’s invited didn’t get through to us. No hard feelings. Can’t believe we missed out on Jason Derulo, though. That stings a little.

Also, big shoutout to @skyler.fulton who directed this bad boy. And who is, by all measures, our absolute boy. We’ll get to Dooley eventually. This is our promise.

Love, 
Jack, Max, Sam (and Intern Pierre) 🤝

node.text:
Here’s the deal. @budlight made us these unreal custom coolers this summer. We got really hyped, so we made a movie. It’s dropping on Thursday. And here’s the fun wrinkle… we’re giving 4 of these bad boys away. All you gotta do is comment and tag your crew on this post, the trailer tomorrow, and the video on Thursday. These are the ultimate suckdown machines, good luck.

Starring superstar @kirkfox 🤝
